      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.247-28</ph> Contractor’s Invoices.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3706e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="47.207-9.dita#FAR_47_207_9"
                     base="i1071172"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">47.207-9</xref>(c)</ph>, insert the following clause in solicitations and contracts for drayage or other term con- tracts for transportation or for transportation-related services:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3706e15">Contractor’s Invoices <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Apr 1984)</ph>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The Contractor shall submit itemized invoices as instructed by the agency ordering services under this contract. The Contractor shall annotate each invoice with the contract number and other ordering office document identification.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
